<td align="center"><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E4%BA%8C" class="extiw" title="wikt:二">二</a></td>
<td><a href="/wiki/2_(number)" title="2 (number)">2</a></td>
<td align="center">èr</td>
<td>also <a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E5%BC%8D" class="extiw" title="wikt:弍">弍</a> (obsolete financial), can be easily manipulated into 弌 (one) or 弎 (three).<br />
also <a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E5%85%A9" class="extiw" title="wikt:兩">兩</a>(T) or <a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E4%B8%A4" class="extiw" title="wikt:两">两</a>(S), see <a href="#Characters_with_regional_usage" title="">Characters with regional usage</a> section.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center"><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E5%8F%84" class="extiw" title="wikt:叄">叄</a>(T) or<br />
<a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E5%8F%81" class="extiw" title="wikt:叁">叁</a>(S)</td>
<td align="center"><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E4%B8%89" class="extiw" title="wikt:三">三</a></td>
<td><a href="/wiki/3_(number)" title="3 (number)">3</a></td>
<td align="center">sān</td>
<td>also <a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E5%BC%8E" class="extiw" title="wikt:弎">弎</a> (obsolete financial), can be easily manipulated into 弌 (one) or 弍 (two).<br />
also <a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E5%8F%83" class="extiw" title="wikt:參">參</a>(T) or <a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E5%8F%82" class="extiw" title="wikt:参">参</a>(S) sān.</td>
