</table>
<p><a name="Small_numbers" id="Small_numbers"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Chinese_numerals&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Small numbers">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Small numbers</span></h4>
<p>The following are characters used to denote small <a href="/wiki/Order_of_magnitude" title="Order of magnitude">order of magnitude</a> in Chinese historically. With the introduction of SI units, some of them have been incorporated as SI prefixes, while the rest have fallen into disuse.</p>
